<h4><a href="https://hypebeast.cn/2020/9/mandalorian-themed-polaroid-now-camera-child-inspired-instant-film-news">宝丽来推出《The Mandalorian》主题拍立得相机</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1368504" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/mandalorian-themed-polaroid-now-camera-child-inspired-instant-film-news-1.jpg" alt="" width="1400" height="933" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/mandalorian-themed-polaroid-now-camera-child-inspired-instant-film-news-1.jpg 1400w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/mandalorian-themed-polaroid-now-camera-child-inspired-instant-film-news-1-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/mandalorian-themed-polaroid-now-camera-child-inspired-instant-film-news-1-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/mandalorian-themed-polaroid-now-camera-child-inspired-instant-film-news-1-1024x682.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1400px) 100vw, 1400px" /></p>
<p>Hypebeast 消息，宝丽来推出《The Mandalorian》主题拍立得相机 Polaroid Now，在相机机身上融入了合金元素装饰，采用了磨砂灰黑色调。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1368505" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/mandalorian-themed-polaroid-now-camera-child-inspired-instant-film-news-7.jpg" alt="" width="1400" height="933" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/mandalorian-themed-polaroid-now-camera-child-inspired-instant-film-news-7.jpg 1400w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/mandalorian-themed-polaroid-now-camera-child-inspired-instant-film-news-7-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/mandalorian-themed-polaroid-now-camera-child-inspired-instant-film-news-7-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/mandalorian-themed-polaroid-now-camera-child-inspired-instant-film-news-7-1024x682.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1400px) 100vw, 1400px" /></p>
<p>此外，宝丽来也推出了《The Mandalorian》主题限量版彩色底片，当中涵盖 Baby Yoda、The Child、Mandarorian 和标志性图像等 8 款设计。</p>
<h4><a href="http://news.mtime.com/2020/09/24/1604122.html">索金新剧《芝加哥七君子审判》发布终极中字预告</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1368506" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/eddi.jpg" alt="" width="1024" height="682" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/eddi.jpg 1024w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/eddi-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/eddi-768x512.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></p>
<p>时光网消息，由《白宫群英》《新闻编辑室》主创艾伦・索金自编自导的新作《芝加哥七君子审判》发布终极中字预告，将于 10 月 16 日在 Netflix 上线。</p>
<p><iframe src="https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=p31557x99i5" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen="allowfullscreen"></iframe></p>
<p>影片改编自 1969 年「芝加哥七君子审判」真实历史事件。这起案件引起全美对司法伦理和法庭秩序的反思，美国也因此案件更加注重司法独立的重要性，本案成为美国着名的民权运动案例。</p>
<h3><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1293890" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/wangyo.png" alt="" width="1029" height="180" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/wangyo.png 1029w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/wangyo-360x63.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/wangyo-768x134.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/wangyo-1024x179.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1029px) 100vw, 1029px" /></h3>
<h4><a href="https://s.weibo.com/weibo?q=%23%E5%85%A8%E5%9B%BD%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%80%E6%9D%A15G%E6%AD%A5%E8%A1%8C%E8%A1%97%23&amp;Refer=top">全国第一条 5G 步行街</a></h4>
<p>广州市北京路步行街经过改造提升，9 月 23 日晚上正式开街，超过十万名市民游客来到现场逛街。</p>
<p>改造升级后的北京路是全国第一条 5G 步行街，沿路可以看到无人清扫机器人、安防巡逻机器人 24 小时自动巡逻、无人售货车等。</p>
<p>网友：「北京路改造后太好逛了，传统文化与现代科技完美融合，有声有色有美食。」「虽然我手机卡是 5G 的，但手机却只用得起 4G 手机。」</p>
<h3><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1357583" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/fri.png" alt="" width="1029" height="153" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/fri.png 1029w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/fri-360x54.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/fri-768x114.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/fri-1024x152.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1029px) 100vw, 1029px" /></h3>
<h4><a href="https://www.thepaper.cn/newsDetail_forward_9212309">一起看个展：《呐喊与回响》</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1368440" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/914.jpg" alt="" width="1080" height="1622" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/914.jpg 1080w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/914-360x541.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/914-768x1153.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/914-682x1024.jpg 682w" sizes="(max-width: 1080px) 100vw, 1080px" /></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/11/72x72/1f4cd.png" alt="📍" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" />  上海久事美术馆 @ 上海</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/11/72x72/231b.png" alt="⌛" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" />   2020.9.25 &#8211; 2021.1.3</p>
<p>《呐喊与回响 —— 爱德华・蒙克版画及油画展（2020 冈德森收藏）》带来了 53 件蒙克创作的油画和版画原作。其中，还包括了蒙克唯一手工上色版的《呐喊》。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1368451" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/care.jpg" alt="" width="1589" height="1062" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/care.jpg 1589w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/care-360x241.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/care-768x513.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/care-1024x684.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1589px) 100vw, 1589px" /></p>
